<h2>Glossary of Terms</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Market Growth Rate:</strong> The annual growth percentage of the market in which the business unit operates.</li>
<li><strong>Relative Market Share:</strong> The market share of the business unit compared to its largest competitor.</li>
