<h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2>
<h3>What is the BCG Matrix?</h3>
<p>The BCG Matrix is a framework to evaluate the strategic position of the business brand portfolio and its potential.</p>
<h3>How do I interpret the results?</h3>
<p>The matrix identifies four categories: Stars, Cash Cows, Question Marks, and Dogs. Each category suggests a different strategy.</p>
